Comment: Two Knights' defense by the book so far... I mostly play Nxf7, Kxf7, Qf3+, and see where this will lead me; best now is probably Ke6!?, Nc3; however, Nce7 is much safer... recommended here is the Fischer line d4!, Be7, Nxf7, Kxf7, Qf3+, with roughly the same results; I should try that one time... this time however, I tried something else; soon to my regret...
